<h6 class="heading"><span class="type">Paragraph</span></h6>
<p>Show that in general, if we let <span class="process-math">\(\int\dx{v}=v+a\)</span>  in the integration by parts formula, then we will obtain the same result as before, namely <span class="process-math">\(\int u\dx{v}=uv-\int v\dx{u}\text{.}\)</span></p>
<span class="incontext"><a href="section-5.html#p-102" class="internal">in-context</a></span>
